            <title>[LU-18493] kernel update [RHEL 8.10 4.18.0-553.30.1.el8_10]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18493</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: media: edia: dvbdev: fix a use-after-free (CVE-2024-27043)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: Bluetooth: l2cap: fix null-ptr-deref in l2cap_chan_timeout (CVE-2024-27399)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: bpf: Add BPF_PROG_TYPE_CGROUP_SKB attach type enforcement in BPF_LINK_CREATE (CVE-2024-38564)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: mptcp: pm: Fix uaf in __timer_delete_sync (CVE-2024-46858)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


